label: Participant ID
description: Anonymous participant identifier (7 participants with no meal data excluded from original 466)

label: Body Mass Index
description: Body Mass Index calculated from weight and height

label: Waist Circumference
description: Waist circumference measured at umbilicus level

label: Food Intake Quality
description: Dietary quality category from Mini-ECCA v.2
column10: a validated 14-item questionnaire for Mexican students. Uses discriminant analysis to classify dietary patterns based on adherence to dietary recommendations.

label: Chronotype
description: Circadian preference based on MEQ questionnaire

label: Breakfast Time
description: Habitual breakfast time in decimal hours

label: Lunch Time
description: Habitual lunch time in decimal hours

label: Dinner Time
description: Habitual dinner time in decimal hours

label: Eating Window
description: Duration from first to last meal

label: Overnight Fasting
description: Duration from last meal to first meal next day

label: Breakfast-Lunch Interval
description: Time interval between breakfast and lunch

label: Lunch-Dinner Interval
description: Time interval between lunch and dinner
